    "text": "Improving Law Enforcement Officer Safety and Wellness Through Data Act\n\nThis bill requires the Department of Justice to report on (1) targeted attacks on law enforcement officers, (2) the feasibility of incorporating such attacks into existing crime reporting systems, and (3) the mental health resources that are available to law enforcement officers."
